        "mainbody": "'''Zerafex''' was a dangerous [[vampire]] who plagued [[Faerûn]] sometime before the mid-14{{th}} century [[DR]].",
        "History": "Zerafex assembled a number of [[vampire spawn]]s under her control at some point long before the {{Yearlink|1368}}. She attracted attention of a [[waterdeep|Waterdhavian]] [[paladin]] of [[Lathander]] named [[Ariabel]]. The paladin carried his [[enchanted]] blade ''[[Harrower]]'' into battle but Zerafex emerged victorious, ending Ariabel's life. Ariabel's corse and ''Harrower'' remained undisturbed for years within a [[Tethyr]]ean crypt where the battle ended."
